dct_description_sm: Map shows roads, populated areas, shantytowns, cemetery, and notable features. Includes a glossary, city location map, and boundary diagram. "Map information as of 1992." "This map is red-light readable." "This sheet falls within NB 38-3, 1501, 1:250,000 and NB 38-47, Y630, 1:100,000." "NIMA ref. no. Y921XGAALKACYO." "NSN 7643014033785." "Caution: This product may not conform to the horizontal accuracy requirements. Extreme caution should be used when making measurements." ©Copyright 1992 by the United States Government.
